accabees-All-Points-East-support-acts-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TheMaccabees-All-Points-East-support-acts-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TheMaccabees-All-Points-East-support-acts-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/TheMaccabees-All-Points-East-support-acts-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-maccabees">马卡比乐队 (The Maccabees)</a>宣布将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/all-points-east">2025 年 All Points East</a>举办的大型重聚演出中进行首次支持表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-maccabees-announce-huge-reunion-show-for-all-point-east-2025-buy-tickets-3806881">正如本周早些时候所证实的</a>，这支伦敦乐队将于 8 月 24 日在首都维多利亚公园登台，这是他们八年来的首次合作演出。这场演出恰逢他们的第四张也是最后一张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/the-maccabees-track-by-track-guide-to-their-fearless-new-album-marks-to-prove-it-762993">“Marks To Prove It”</a>发行十周年。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/86tvs-on-john-mcenroe-starring-in-rage-video-for-new-single-komorebi-he-was-screaming-in-my-face-3773270">86TVs 播出约翰·麦肯罗 (John McEnroe) 主演的新单曲《Komorebi》的“愤怒视频”：“他在我面前尖叫！”</a></strong></li></ul><p>据透露，The Maccabees 将与 All Points East 合作策划当天的完整阵容，其中包括“他们喜爱的新老艺术家”。</p><p>现在，第一波开放艺术家已以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bombay-bicycle-club">Bombay Bicycle Club</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cribs">The Cribs</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dry-cleaning">Dry Cleaning</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nilufer-yanya">Nilüfer Yanya</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-murder-capital">The Murder Capital</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/divorce-announce-debut-album-drive-to-goldenhammer-with-insert-word-phrase-here-new-single-all-my-freaks-use-this-headline-nme-radar-3796610">Divorce</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/prima-queen">Prima Queen</a>的形式共享。</p><p>组织者承诺，未来几个月将宣布更多活动。马卡比队的大逆转标志着明年东点赛的首个阵容公布。</p><p>门票将于格林威治标准时间明天（10 月 31 日星期四）上午 10 点开始公开发售 – <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3DThe%2BMaccabees" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里购买</a>。另外，<a href="http://www.themaccabees.co.uk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">已报名预售的</a>粉丝也可以在今天同一时间（10 月 30 日星期三）购买门票。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBvoC7AIjwN/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.8